---
title: Parsley & Garlic Beef Bistro with Spiced Potatoes, Lemony Greens & Hazelnuts
description: You don’t have to wait for a special occasion to create this fine-dining dish. We’ve taken the delectable combination of tender
beef bistro and parsley-garlic sauce, then added a few special touches - crispy chunks of roasted potato, earthy hazelnuts and
creamy goat cheese. Just add a glass of wine and enjoy!
